Will DEFINITELY be Back!!! Seriously tasty, and well seasoned burger. What I liked off the bat... when I called in the order, she let me be picky and choosy. The young lady that answered pretty much let me make my crazy burger my way...AND... I couldn't believe it was for such a reasonable price. Those other "Guys" would've charged double and it wouldn't have tasted as good. They also let me order it medium. In a world of fast casual spots popping up everywhere it was refreshing to find a home grown mom & pop, or in this case cousins, who run a great spot in my backyard. Loved it and WILL DEFINITELY BE BACK!!! #LetsGuide #BurgerShack #RecoveringKnowItAll #GreatBurgers
